: null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O He Who is Ever-living and never dies, (please) send blessings upon Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad, forgive my sins that I have committed between You and me, do not expose me in the presence of the witnesses, guard me with Your Eye that never sleeps, You as me upon mercy have and have full power over me. O most merciful of all those who show mercy! May Allah send blessings upon our master Muhammad and upon his Immaculate Household. O Lord of the worlds!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay zindah jise maut nahi Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) par rehmat farma aur mere gunah maaf kar de jo mere aur Tere darmiyaan hai, mujhe logo’n ke saamne ruswa na kar, meri nigheh-daari kar un aankho’n se jo soti nahi hai aur rahem kar apni qudrat se jo Tu mujh par rakhta hai, ay sab se ziyadah rahem karne waale aur Khuda rahem farmaaye hamare sardaar Muhammad (s.a.w.a) par aur unki paakeeza Aal (a.s) par, ay jahano ke Parwardigaar.", "Urdu": "اے زندہ جسے موت نہیں محمدؐ وآل محمدؑ پر رحمت فرما اور میرے گناہ معاف کردے جو میرےاور تیرے درمیان ہیں مجھے لوگوں کے سامنے رسوا نہ کر میری نگہداری کر ان آنکھوں سے جو سوتی نہیں ہیں اور رحم کر اپنی قدرت سے جو تو مجھ پر رکھتاہے اے سب سے زیادہ رحم کرنے والے اور خدا رحم فرمائے ہمارے سردار محمدؐ پر اور ان کی پاکیزہ آلؑ پر اے جہانوں کے پروردگار۔", "RArabic": "YAA HAYYAN LAA YAMOOTO SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIWN WA AALE MOHAMMADIWN WAGH-FIR LEYAZ ZONOOBAL LATEE BAYNEE WA BAYNAKA WA LAA TAF-ZAHNEE A’LAA RO-OOOSIL ASH-HAADE WAH-RUS-NEE BE-A’YNEKAL LATEE LAA TANAAMO WAR-HAMNEE BE-QUDRATEKA A’LAYYA YAA ARHAMAR RAAHEMEENA WA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAA SAYYEDENAA MOHAMMADIWN WA AALEHIT TAAHEREENA YAA RABBAL A’ALAMEEN.", "ArabicText1": "یَا حَیًّا لَا یَمُوْتُ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاغْفِرْ لِیَ الذُّنُوْبَ الَّتِیْ بَیْنِیْ وَبَیْنَكَ وَلَا تَفْضَحْنِیْ عَلٰی رُؤُوْسِ الْاَشْھَادِ وَاحْرُسْنِیْ بِعَیْنِكَ الَّتِیْ لَا تَنَامُ وَارْحَمْنِیْ بِقُدْرَتِكَ عَلَیَّ یَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِیْنَ وَصَلَّی اللہُ عَلٰی سَیِّدِنَا مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِهِ الطَّاھِرِیْنَ یَا رَبَّ الْعَالَمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null